        [accordion=600]
            {slide=Trainer TLDR}
            1. Trainers are required to have a League-certified means of identification.
            2. Trainers are not limited to carrying 6 pokémon, but you do so at your own inconvenience.
            3. Trainers are required to obtain a 'Ride License' before using pokémon as mounts or transport. 
            {/slide}
